{
  "stem": "7938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came in to all the houses and told the people that they have to give all the furs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't be allowed to have furs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they came in once, and they-- we have to give back some money, but this was later.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't-- from the beginning, there was no ordnungsdienst.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yet.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a little bit later, they created it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Judenrat received order, whatever order the Germans wanted to give, except the first one, that they-- that they told that everybody had to have arm bands with the Jewish sign on them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except this one, which the governor gave out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anything what they wanted, if they wanted some money to be collected, if they wanted-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to the Judenrat, and the Judenrat had to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was like a-- there was a German SS officer who was especially assigned for this to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was a Jewish hospital near the Judenrat place, where it was before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a Jewish hospital which had all facilities, and everything which was needed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well this situation existed until the ghetto was supposed to be opened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until the ghetto was supposed to be started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the next year, in 1940, they already announced that there will be a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ghetto will be only people who have an interest to be in Cracow-- or there in the ghetto-- will be put in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest wouldn't have-- wouldn't have the permission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody was, was afraid what they will do with the other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they told them that they can go and to live in the little villages around Cracow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, they had to-- they looked for work, to work somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
